  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Registration of clinical trials for investigational medicinal products and publication of summary results from 1 January 2021
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">This guidance contains information about registration of clinical trials, publishing trial results and future requirements from 1 January 2021.</p>

  </div>
</div>

